# Frontend dropdowns

- Prefer **`SelectKeeper`** (`frontend/src/components/SelectKeeper.tsx`) for single-choice dropdowns so styling matches the app theme (`select-keeper` styles in `index.css`: primary tint, orange hovers).
- Use **`MultiSelectKeeper`** when multiple selections are needed.
- Avoid raw **`<select>`** on new screens unless there is a strong accessibility or platform reason; if you must use native controls, isolate them and align spacing with neighbouring `SelectKeeper` triggers.
